***CB Amplifier Design Using NgSpice***


Step 1:Create File
Open terminal: type command below 
nano cb_amp.cir

Step 2:In GNU Dashboard Paste below Script
* Common Base Amplifier

VCC vcc 0 DC 12

VB base 0 DC 2

VIN in 0 SIN(0 0.01 1k)

RC vcc collector 4.7k
RE emitter in 1k

Q1 collector base emitter 2N3904

.model 2N3904 NPN(IS=6.734E-15 BF=255.9)

.tran 0.1ms 10ms

.control
run
plot v(in) v(collector)
.endc

.end

Step 3:Run Simulation
ngspice cb_amp.cir

You can observe waveform and OutPut in Terminal.
